        <title>Project hosting with Launchpad</title>
        <paragraph><reference name="Launchpad" refuri="http://launchpad.net">Launchpad</reference> hosts the manila project. The manila project homepage on Launchpad is
            <reference refuri="http://launchpad.net/manila">http://launchpad.net/manila</reference>.</paragraph>
